    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 era. The powerplant retains its 8,400 RPM redline integrity, with rod bearings and throttle actuators proactively serviced to ensure long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis maintains its composure thanks to functional Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and refreshed suspension bushings. No subframe fatigue is present, and the hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and leak-free. A driver-focused machine with the visceral induction note of individual throttle bodies, ready for immediate enthusiast use.",
