      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable and well-cared-for vehicle that strikes an excellent balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the interior is impressively clean; the seats are free of tears or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and premium audio system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the car is mechanically robust with a consistent maintenance history. It starts up immediately, idles smoothly, and handles the road with precision. We recently completed a full fluid flush and tire rotation, ensuring it is turn-key ready for its next owner. This is an honest, solid car that looks great and performs even better.",
