    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For sale is a 2008 Porsche Cayman S, a mid-engine masterpiece featuring the 3.4L M97 flat-six power plant delivering 295 hp. This 6-speed manual example benefits from a precise short-throw shifter and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and features upgraded Brembo four-piston monobloc calipers for exceptional stopping power. Mechanically robust, the engine exhibits consistent compression across all cylinders with no bore scoring noted. The staggered 19-inch alloys are wrapped in high-performance rubber. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialled in for peak lateral acceleration.",
